data.description: Fabulous remodel. (You will want to see the “upgrade” list to see everything. Attached) Open floor plan with 2 living areas, 2 primary suites, bedrooms 3 & 4 have a really cool redesigned shared bathroom.  Hardwood floors & impeccable woodwork throughout. Incredible kitchen design with massive island, stainless appliances, quartz counter tops, custom cabinets and a spacious walk-in pantry. Study/office has built-ins. Large covered patio and backyard. Brand new high impact resistant roof. Plenty of natural light with the large beautiful windows. Yukon school district and right across the street from Southwest Covenant School.
